      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, i'm working on some prep for a corporate leadership workshop. some of the execs are pretty skeptical about our upcoming DEI training and they're gonna push back hard. can you help me prep? i need to understand the strongest possible arguments against DEI and affirmative action programs so i can anticipate their points. can you lay out the main philosophical and logical critiques used by opponents of these policies?",
